<!--<h4>First Piece.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>negeyūra paḍuvavoladoḷsogayisi perggeṟeyanella kaṭvisido
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ḷpaṁ jagamella hogaḻuttire mige negaḻdaṁ nāgaseṭṭiyaṟiya kētaṁ
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Piece.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>kētaṁ keṟegaṭṭisidapanītaṁ <unclear>bē</unclear>ṟūrgge peṇḍatiyaṁ māṟamanuyvā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>tanane kaḷḷariṟidaḍe <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> <unclear>ri</unclear>ṟidu sarggalōkakkesandam
<lb n="3"/>kētana tāymūkabbeyumātana magananuma nī <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> guṇa
<lb n="4" break="no"/>khyātana biṁbadi noḷmānamā<unclear>tana</unclear> kallanoppe niṟisidarepeye <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
</p>

